  <h1>Bixby Heart Dot Com</h1>
  <h3>Together with Jake Ingman, we built a web-based iPhone application to help our dear friend Mark Bixby keep an eye on his ticker during SXSW 2008. By choosing to feed him bacon or juice, the crowd had control over Mark&#8217;s delicious fate.</h3>
